{"title":"“十一”抒情","authors":["臧克家"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":10,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“十一”抒情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"臧克家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门升高了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻纱般的云彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作了大红宫灯的飘带。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长安街更长了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广场更加宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢腾腾人流像春水涨满。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门前人不断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步接着脚步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国连成一条线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼声浪无遮拦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像海心的波浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扩展到地角天边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"礼花像万箭冲天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一注注眼光一颗颗心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四方八面聚拢在一点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临别西山的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你曾经再三相约："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“十一”那天重来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山头上并肩看焰火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天我留在城里边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作欢腾大海里的浪花一朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩头让给孩子坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从房顶高处看缤纷红雨落。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当大队用雄健的步子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏得大地震动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可曾听到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从英雄纪念碑上发出的回声？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当万众振臂欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拳头像信心一般坚强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可曾注目"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄碑上举起的英雄胳膀？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当歌声舞影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在月光灯光下响动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可曾仿佛看到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍巍石碑上飘落下一个个身影？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}